@56263 = ~*Your WILL is strong. Your DISCIPLINE is strong. Your WILL is the will of LAW.*~ [VH56263V]
@56265 = ~*KNOW THIS: There is nothing on ALL the PLANES that can STAY the hand of JUSTICE when it is brought against them. It may unmake ARMIES. It may sunder the thrones of GODS. When your cause is JUSTICE, JUSTICE will lend you its STRENGTH.*~ [VH56265V]
@56267 = ~*You do NOT see. NOT yet. Open your eyes to me, and you shall SEE the PLANES through the eyes of JUSTICE.*~ [VH56267V]
