@56315 = ~*I... remember.* Vhailor's eyes flicker, more erratic than before. His axe falls to his side. *The memory is... DIFFICULT to remember. There was a DEATH... and I have CHANGED. I am not that ONE any longer. What AM I?*~ [VH56315V]
@56320 = ~*JUSTICE was my cause. The FLESH... the FLESH could not remain. Yet JUSTICE needed to be SERVED. There was the DEATH of flesh, but the WILL would not let go... there were MORE to be punished. ALWAYS more. JUSTICE... JUSTICE would not have been served by my DEATH.*~ [VH56320V]
