@56670 = ~Vhailor stares at you, his eyes burning brightly. You feel the same *stare* as before, the tearing and peeling back of the skin, as Vhailor seems to dissect you. You feel a wave of nausea swim through you, and a sense of *drowning,* deeper this time... until your vision almost fades to black...~ [VH56670V]
